## Purpose

This checklist makes a recurring process repeatable. Following the steps in order is not optional; the order encodes lessons learned from earlier runs.

If a step turns out to be wrong, fix the step in the same pull request that proves the fix works. Do not skip steps to save time and tell yourself you will go back.

